Package: Rdataxm
Title: Access Colombian Energy Market Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Victor", "Sarmiento", , "victorsarmiento8@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides access to Colombian energy market data from XM (SINERGOX)
    and SIMEM APIs. Includes functionality for retrieving time series data,
    metadata, and performing data normalization.
